    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEMESIS DISTRESS</strong> is a unique multiplayer Sci-Fi horror experience that aims at creating unforgettable, cinematic moments. Remember – this is NOT a shooter, in Nemesis you are not the hunter. You are the PREY.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you can hope to achieve is to survive and complete your secret objective as well as main mission. But beware – in multiplayer experience you are not playing a full co-op. Any other player MIGHT be a traitor and will aim at sabotaging you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak your way around the ship, find useful items, take advantage of the noise mechanic and all the tricks around the ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Horror experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/e82ddf3a8d9ef90e052dc4aec48a08f6.poster.avif?t=1771506660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/e82ddf3a8d9ef90e052dc4aec48a08f6.webm?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/e82ddf3a8d9ef90e052dc4aec48a08f6.mp4?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We wanted to craft a really thrilling environment, where every sound and movement around the ship will get you on the edge of your sit. There are different types of enemies, with the most dangerous Adult, that can one-shot you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique semi co-op</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/d8aa70c8945488c2da1222d250539683.poster.avif?t=1771506660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/d8aa70c8945488c2da1222d250539683.webm?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/d8aa70c8945488c2da1222d250539683.mp4?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to find a fine balance between collaborating with your team-mates (as otherwise you will not survive) and not trusting them fully, as some of them might have some nasty secret objectives. This creates an interesting dynamic and add a bit of extra layer on the horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Noise management</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/2dd788d06b3f25d908c6a272adfe05f4.poster.avif?t=1771506660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/2dd788d06b3f25d908c6a272adfe05f4.webm?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/2dd788d06b3f25d908c6a272adfe05f4.mp4?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since the alien species on the ship is blind, you will need to be very careful about the sound that you make. But you can also use it to your advantage -  throw items to distract enemies and sneak past them…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >… or just use flamethrower to scare them away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fresh items idea</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/cf8b13774bd066bacc3a78aa7bbe5f56.poster.avif?t=1771506660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/cf8b13774bd066bacc3a78aa7bbe5f56.webm?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343620/extras/cf8b13774bd066bacc3a78aa7bbe5f56.mp4?t=1771506660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since Nemesis is not a shooter, don’t expect too many weapons. Instead, you will have a different “arsenal” – noise detector, hacking tool or good-old pipe will come in handy in various situations.</p>",
